  "story": {
    "text": {
      "en": "The morning's CRM bugs got promoted to infrastructure. Rep marks were invisible until the hourly matview bake, so a live_contact overlay now supersedes it on every read, and every contact, follow-up and outreach write lands in a new host_activity_events audit trail (migrations 065–066), guarded by a drift test that reads the migration SQL. Florida's FF listings refreshed in bulk alongside.",
      "fr": "Les bugs CRM du matin sont devenus de l'infrastructure. Les marques des reps restaient invisibles jusqu'à la matview horaire — un overlay live_contact la supplante à chaque lecture, et chaque contact, suivi ou prospection s'inscrit au journal host_activity_events (migrations 065–066), protégé par un test qui lit le SQL des migrations. En parallèle, les annonces FF de la Floride ont été rafraîchies en bloc."
    }
  },
